## Walkthrough

* The player starts standing in Grandmaâ€™s house. She asks you to please plug in her TV. Pick up the power cord and plug it into the outlet. 
* Grandma thanks you. Now, she asks you to please set up her VCR. You now have access to the VCR, its power cord, its video cable, and two audio cables.
* Hook up the VCR to power first. Plug in the power cord to the power strip.
* Next, you can plug in the video cable. Pick up the video cable and plug it into the VCR. Pick up the other end and plug it into the TV.
* Next, pick up the audio cables. One is the left cable, and one is the right. Plug them into the corresponding ports in the VCR, and then plug the other ends into the TV.
